      "author": "AyWutiansui",
      "description": "## What's New in v1.3.0\n\n### Context-Aware Search\n- Search is now scoped to the current notebook or section when one is selected\n- Search heading shows the scope (e.g. `5 results for \"math\" in \"School\"`)\n- Search placeholder updates dynamically to show current scope\n- Search result count displayed in heading (e.g. \"3 results for...\")\n- Empty search restores the appropriate view level (pages/sections/notebooks)\n\n### Keyboard Shortcuts\n- **Ctrl+F / Cmd+F** — Focus the search bar\n- **Escape** — Clear search and restore current view\n- **Enter / Space** — Activate focused list items (already in v1.2.0)\n\n### Workflow Enhancements\n- **Copy Link** button copies `onenote:` URL to clipboard\n- **Insert button** (plus-circle icon, appears on hover) inserts a ` ```onenote ` code block at the cursor position\n- Status bar shows OneNote connection status at a glance\n- Refresh button updates status bar indicator\n\n### Error Handling\n- Page content loading errors now show a Retry button\n- Error messages include contextual icons\n\n### Build\n- Bundle: ~60KB (minified)\n- TypeScript: 0 errors\n- Tests: 77/77 passing",
      "downloadCount": 0,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "v1.3.0 — Smart Search & Workflow Enhancements",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2026-06-18T11:21:12Z",
      "tag": "v1.3.0"
