      "author": "AyWutiansui",
      "description": "## What's New in v1.2.0\n\n### Sidebar Improvements\n- Lucide icons on notebook/section/page list items (book/folder/file-text)\n- Pages sorted by modification time (newest first)\n- Date badges on page items showing last modified date\n- Child count badges on notebooks and sections\n- Fade-in animation on view transitions\n- Keyboard accessibility (role=button, tabindex, Enter/Space navigation)\n- Focus-visible outlines for keyboard users\n- Truncated names show full text on hover (title tooltip)\n- Search text highlighting with `<mark>` elements\n- Icon buttons in header (compact, with tooltips)\n- Breadcrumb navigation with Lucide icon\n- Improved empty states with icons, hints, and action buttons\n- Page content displays with title bar and file-text icon\n- \"Open in OneNote\" button with external-link icon\n- Responsive layout for narrow sidebars\n\n### Code Block Improvements\n- Dropdown labels with contextual icons\n- Debounced Detach/Attach button (prevents race conditions)\n- Loading state feedback on Load Page button\n- Error states with alert icons\n- Theme-aware iframe with prefers-color-scheme\n- Inline style cleanup → CSS classes\n\n### Accessibility\n- All interactive elements have role/tabindex/keyboard handlers\n- Focus-visible outlines on clickable elements\n- Label `for`/select `id` pairing on dropdowns\n- ARIA labels on interactive elements\n\n### Bug Fixes\n- manifest.json: isDesktopOnly set to true (COM dependency)\n- Removed stale get-notebooks.ps1 reference from build config\n- compile-repos.bat: added win-embed-overlay.c compilation\n\n### Build\n- Bundle size: ~58KB (minified)\n- All 77 tests passing\n- TypeScript: 0 errors",
      "downloadCount": 0,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "v1.2.0 — Frontend UI Overhaul",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2026-06-18T11:09:52Z",
