      "author": "AyWutiansui",
      "description": "## What's new in v1.1.0\n\n### Bug Fixes\n- **`isDesktopOnly`** now correctly set to `true` (plugin requires COM/AppleScript)\n- Removed stale `get-notebooks.ps1` reference from esbuild config\n- Added `win-embed-overlay.c` compilation to `compile-repos.bat`\n\n### New Features\n- **Default Notebook**: setting now auto-opens the matching notebook on sidebar load\n- **Cache Refresh**: new ↻ Refresh button to clear the 5-min hierarchy cache\n- **Search**: cross-hierarchy fuzzy search (notebooks, sections, pages) with 200ms debounce\n- **Page dates**: last modified date shown next to each page in sidebar\n\n### UX Improvements\n- **Breadcrumb navigation** replaces old Back buttons (📓 Notebooks › Notebook › Section › Page)\n- **Loading spinners** with CSS animation replace plain text loading messages\n- **Child counts**: badge showing section/page counts on notebook and section items\n- **iframe HTML shell**: page content wrapped in proper DOCTYPE/charset/viewport\n- **Inline style cleanup**: all hardcoded styles moved to CSS classes using Obsidian theme variables\n- **Flex header**: buttons and platform info properly aligned",
